✅ No existing functionality was modified or broken

## Next Steps

After deployment to Vercel:
1. Enable Web Analytics in the Vercel dashboard under Project Settings → Analytics
2. After the next deployment, analytics routes will be available at `/_vercel/insights/*`
3. Visit any page on the deployed site to verify the analytics are tracking (check browser Network tab for requests to `/_vercel/insights/view`)
4. View analytics data in the Vercel dashboard under the Analytics tab

## Notes

- The Analytics component works automatically in production environments when deployed to Vercel
- In development mode, it operates in a test mode that doesn't send real data
- Route tracking is automatic due to the integration with react-router-dom
- The implementation follows the official Vercel documentation for React applications
